# Content Processing Scripts

This directory contains automation scripts for the content pipeline:

## Core Scripts

- `catalogSourceMaterials.js` - Content inventory and indexing
- `prepare_for_ocr.py` - PDF preprocessing for OCR
- `extract_structure.py` - Document structure extraction
- `rewriteContent.js` - AI-powered content rewriting
- `generateQuizzes.js` - Automated assessment creation
- `generateAudio.js` - Audio narration generation
- `createSubjectBundle.js` - Content packaging

## Helper Scripts

- `logger.js` - Centralized logging utility
- `promptTemplates.js` - AI prompt templates
- `curriculumHelper.js` - Curriculum alignment tools
- `contentValidator.js` - Quality assurance checks
- `quizValidator.js` - Assessment validation
- `examPatternHelper.js` - WASSCE pattern analysis

## Usage

```bash
# Install dependencies
npm install
pip install -r requirements.txt

# Run individual scripts
node scripts/catalogSourceMaterials.js
python scripts/prepare_for_ocr.py

# Run complete pipeline
npm run pipeline
```